---
layout: base.njk
description: "How AI is affecting the practice of science. A weekly curated link roundup by Leo Torres."
---

<div class="archive-header">
    <p class="archive-description">How AI is affecting the practice of science. Weekly.</p>
</div>

{% set editions = collections.edition | reverse %}
{% if editions.length %}
<ul class="edition-list">
    {% for post in editions %}
    <li>
        <a href="{{ post.url }}">
            <span class="edition-list-number">No. {{ post.data.number | padStart(3) }}</span>
            <span class="edition-list-date">{{ post.date | dateFormat }}</span>
        </a>
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
</ul>
{% else %}
<p>First edition coming soon.</p>
{% endif %}
